This could be fixed by changing line 41 of "args.cc" from:

loss = loss_name::softmax;

to: 

loss = loss_name::ns;

Note also: "-loss" is the only hyperparameter whose value is not streamed into the doc string (line 140 of "args.cc"), which is perhaps how the error occurred.

